description: You only need 5 ingredients to whip up these easy Mexican-inspired tacos. Ready in just 20 minutes, this recipe uses pre-cooked chicken to save you time in the kitchen.
name: Roast Chicken & Avocado Ranch Slaw Tacos Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Shred chicken, discarding skin and bones. Place coleslaw in a bowl, then drizzle with dressing and scatter over feta from the kit.
Heat a barbecue plate or a large frying over medium heat. Cook tortillas for 30 seconds on each side or until just golden.
Place coleslaw and chicken along centres of tortillas, top with coriander and jalapeno, fold to enclose filling, then serve.
